    <h1>Welcome to VG Tracker!</h1>
      This website helps to track your video game purchases.  Ever had multiple copies of a game because you purchased them via different sources or for several platforms?  This site hopes to alleviate those very issues!
      <br /> <br />
      If a game doesn't exist in our database yet, the site will pull from the IGDB API for video games and add the game(s) to our database.
      <br /><br />
      If you'd like to manually add a game to the database, just contact us and give us as much information as you can.  Once we confirm all the details, we can add it and let you know.
